message:
Setup project structure/files

+ cleanup app component

Add & configure rescripts dependency

So we can load translations file from public directory (for test/dev purpose)

Ensure that firefox build contains extension id

id is required on self install/update + on auto release to amo

Write unit tests for Blocked component

+ Updated App component test

Added @types/jest dependency

+ make test:all command verbose

Update package.json

Make unit tests console output verbose

Update package.json

Add script to package source files

Downgrade react-scripts dependency to v3

@see https://stackoverflow.com/a/65707301

Open settings in a new tab by default

To fix settings dialog size issues on Edge

Update build config #20

+ Disabled source map files generation (because generated paths inside map files may differ depending on build location which cause build artifacts to be different)

Update package.json

postbuild scripts runs automatically after build, no need to append them to the build scripts

chore: add sign script

starting from firefox 90, signing extensions is required to be able to install the extension (even locally)

release: v2.5.0

Note: version number 2.4.x was omitted because of submission issues on AMO
feat: ability to generate a random password #29

chore(deps): bump node-sass from 4.14.1 to 7.0.0

Bumps [node-sass](https://github.com/sass/node-sass) from 4.14.1 to 7.0.0.
- [Release notes](https://github.com/sass/node-sass/releases)
- [Changelog](https://github.com/sass/node-sass/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md)
- [Commits](https://github.com/sass/node-sass/compare/v4.14.1...v7.0.0)

---
updated-dependencies:
- dependency-name: node-sass
  dependency-type: direct:production
...

Signed-off-by: dependabot[bot] <support@github.com>

ci: ignore warnings

+ fixed critical ones

chore: replace rescripts with craco

closes #49

chore: copy global third-party libraries from the node_modules folder

instead of using a static version of these libraries

chore(deps): bump got and web-ext

Bumps [got](https://github.com/sindresorhus/got) to 12.5.2 and updates ancestor dependency [web-ext](https://github.com/mozilla/web-ext). These dependencies need to be updated together.


Updates `got` from 8.3.2 to 12.5.2
- [Release notes](https://github.com/sindresorhus/got/releases)
- [Commits](https://github.com/sindresorhus/got/compare/v8.3.2...v12.5.2)

Updates `web-ext` from 6.8.0 to 7.3.1
- [Release notes](https://github.com/mozilla/web-ext/releases)
- [Commits](https://github.com/mozilla/web-ext/compare/6.8.0...7.3.1)

---
updated-dependencies:
- dependency-name: got
  dependency-type: indirect
- dependency-name: web-ext
  dependency-type: direct:development
...

Signed-off-by: dependabot[bot] <support@github.com>
chore: update dependencies to fix some vulnerabilities

chore(dependencies): revert evergreen-ui to an older release

to fix some weird errors on unit tests
